M|Dunn|tx|Complete guide to recovering failed payments and reducing involuntary churn.
M|Dunn|tx|---
M|Why |it|Failed payments cause 30-50% of all subscription churn
M|Why |it|Most failed payments are recoverable w/ the right st
M|Why |it|Subscription businesses lose an estimated $129 billion annually to involuntary churn
M|Why |it|Effective dunning recovers 50-60% of failed payments
